{
  "id": "69c6acef315b8a2a33be234e",
  "title": "2026/03/28(haruhi)",
  "created": 1774628080,
  "updated": 1774794232,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c6acef315b8a2a33be234e",
      "text": "2026/03/28(haruhi)",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628080,
      "updated": 1774628080
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c61900000000007d212d",
      "text": "画像蓋",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700057,
      "updated": 1774700061
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c61d00000000007d212e",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1e144b51cb6486ce90634951f116f368]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700061,
      "updated": 1774700077
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c62c00000000007d2130",
      "text": " [発達障害かもだけど、お金のことちゃんとしたい人の本]にいい挿絵があったので、スクショをとった",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700077,
      "updated": 1774700112
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c61d00000000007d212f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700061,
      "updated": 1774700061
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6ae01000000000084e564",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628353,
      "updated": 1774628353
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6add0000000000084e55e",
      "text": " [もう１ページに全員が日記書くのやめた方がいいんじゃない？]＞infoboxで小分けにして見る　のをやってみたいと思った",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628304,
      "updated": 1774628345
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78f620000000000a7705c",
      "text": " \t結論　infoboxが見ててそんなに楽しくないので微妙",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774686051,
      "updated": 1774686071
    },
    {
      "id": "69c78fec000000000071aba0",
      "text": " \t実況させるのが面白かったのでここでもやってみよう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774686189,
      "updated": 1774686212
    },
    {
      "id": "69c791720000000000455d09",
      "text": " \tうんこ博士に出張させた、すまん",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774686578,
      "updated": 1774686608
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a8400000000000071b78",
      "text": " \tうんこ博士覚醒してきた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774692417,
      "updated": 1774692421
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6ae3f000000000084e568",
      "text": " 1ヶ月くらいみんなで続けてみたらなんか見えてくるかもしれないと思っているが急進的すぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628415,
      "updated": 1774628449
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6c47800000000002b9f59",
      "text": " 長文書く人は意外と少ない説もある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774634104,
      "updated": 1774634104
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6ae6c000000000084e56a",
      "text": " [ページ遷移がめんどい]んだよな",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774628460,
      "updated": 1774651450
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6ae79000000000084e56b",
      "text": " \t紙のノートみたいに左右矢印のボタンでじゅんぐりにページ遷移がしたい可能性がある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628474,
      "updated": 1774628530
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6ae98000000000084e56c",
      "text": "\t 個人プロジェクトの日記はそのようにしているのだがリロードしないとボタンを読み込まない不具合がある。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628505,
      "updated": 1774628530
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6c3ad00000000002b9f53",
      "text": "\t考え中",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774633902,
      "updated": 1774633920
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6c3da00000000002b9f54",
      "text": "\tinfoboxに貫通させるために",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774633946,
      "updated": 1774634011
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6c41a00000000002b9f56",
      "text": "\t一番の話題は次を抜き出せ: 「ここに長文を書いたらinfoboxが拾ってくれたりして」",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774634011,
      "updated": 1774634029
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6c43f00000000002b9f57",
      "text": " \t一覧で見える",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774634048,
      "updated": 1774634377
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6c58600000000002a8cc9",
      "text": " \tネトゲのシャウト的な",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774634374,
      "updated": 1774634374
    },
    {
      "id": "69c935b80000000000ca5130",
      "text": "\t[260328: GTDの不理解(haruhi)]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774794168,
      "updated": 1774794211
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6ccb500000000002a8ce9",
      "text": " これだけ書いたので分離したかいがあった笑",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774636215,
      "updated": 1774794228
    },
    {
      "id": "69c935f40000000000ca5131",
      "text": " \t切り出した。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774794228,
      "updated": 1774794232
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7366200000000004b8693",
      "text": " 大量の[うんこ]を放出した",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774663266,
      "updated": 1774686522
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7386f00000000001d4baa",
      "text": "  [ナイス排便][seibe.icon][Summer498.icon][sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774663791,
      "updated": 1774689432
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7390700000000004b8695",
      "text": "  ありがとう❗️[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774663943,
      "updated": 1774663952
    },
    {
      "id": "69c79d0300000000005a3d0d",
      "text": "\t[/hoshihara]が面白過ぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774689540,
      "updated": 1774689549
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7be1f0000000000f64bd0",
      "text": "\t\tまじか[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1774698014,
      "updated": 1774698018
    },
    {
      "id": "69c79d6d0000000000290127",
      "text": " \t理由はわからない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774689645,
      "updated": 1774690578
    },
    {
      "id": "69c79f630000000000f85db2",
      "text": " \tといいつつ9割くらいは興味ないかも",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690147,
      "updated": 1774690578
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c57500000000007d2129",
      "text": "  \t流し読み未満もしてないかもしれないけど長く巡回ルートに入れている",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774699894,
      "updated": 1774699894
    },
    {
      "id": "69c79f720000000000f85db3",
      "text": " \t自動的にスルーしているが残ったものが面白過ぎる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690162,
      "updated": 1774690578
    },
    {
      "id": "69c79fba0000000000f85db5",
      "text": " \t9割をスルーしやすいということかな、？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690234,
      "updated": 1774690583
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1170000000000f85dbd",
      "text": " \tうんこ博士〜どうなの",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690584,
      "updated": 1774690691
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c57c00000000007d212a",
      "text": " \tなんでもないところが自分の思考回路に似ていて安心するのかもしれない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774699901,
      "updated": 1774699914
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c68600000000007d2131",
      "text": " \t鏡っぽいからじっくり見れない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700167,
      "updated": 1774700175
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1820000000000f85dbf",
      "text": " 2年前のPOPYOURSのニューカマーショットライブ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690691,
      "updated": 1774690704
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1900000000000f85dc0",
      "text": "  https://spincoaster.com/news/pop-yours-2024-new-comer-shot-live",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690704,
      "updated": 1774690706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1920000000000f85dc1",
      "text": "  JAKEN, Kohjiya, L.O.S.T",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690706,
      "updated": 1774690727
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1ab0000000000f85dc4",
      "text": "  CFN MALIK, リルソフ, Swetty, taro",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690731,
      "updated": 1774690747
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1cc0000000000f85dc8",
      "text": "  JAKEN最近あんま目立たないけどビジネスやってるのかな。よくわからない。去年のアルバムには確かPlayssonとかTee Shyneが入ってて人脈が本当によくわからなかった。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690764,
      "updated": 1774691107
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a4f80000000000f85dd7",
      "text": "   目立たないとかいうわけではないっぽい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691576,
      "updated": 1774703093
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7d1f60000000000f636a2",
      "text": "   曲が2パターンしかない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774703095,
      "updated": 1774703125
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7d2920000000000f636a3",
      "text": "   Seaside Swag良すぎるな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774703251,
      "updated": 1774703258
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a3920000000000f85dd3",
      "text": "  Kohjiyaがニューカマーだった時代凄いよな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691219,
      "updated": 1774691219
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a39e0000000000f85dd4",
      "text": "   2024のぽぷゆあだからラップスタア放送中なのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691231,
      "updated": 1774691256
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a3f00000000000f85dd6",
      "text": "   LEXがAbemaくんのクッション蹴ってもう2年になるのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691312,
      "updated": 1774691335
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a3ba0000000000f85dd5",
      "text": "   関係ないけどこのくらいの時期にKohjiyaとかMIKADOがljとアルバム出してた事に関しては良すぎた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691258,
      "updated": 1774691416
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a2080000000000f85dc9",
      "text": "  L.O.S.T って知らん",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690825,
      "updated": 1774690831
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a2600000000000f85dca",
      "text": "  \tああ、M3Rかー",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690914,
      "updated": 1774690923
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1bb0000000000f85dc5",
      "text": "  taroいたの熱いな",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690747,
      "updated": 1774690753
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a1c10000000000f85dc6",
      "text": "   DADAもだけどあんまシーンに出てきていない？",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690753,
      "updated": 1774691115
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a32d0000000000f85dd0",
      "text": "   DADAは2026にも出るのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691117,
      "updated": 1774691121
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ce870000000000f63688",
      "text": "    全然リリースしてないやん",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774702217,
      "updated": 1774702228
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7cec10000000000f6368b",
      "text": "    て言ってたら1時間前にMV出てて神",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774702274,
      "updated": 1774702282
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7cf730000000000f6368c",
      "text": "    https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWT0UW_ZdsM&list=RDBWT0UW_ZdsM&start_radio=1",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774702452,
      "updated": 1774702459
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7cf7e0000000000f6368e",
      "text": "    良",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774702463,
      "updated": 1774702470
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a2ab0000000000f85dce",
      "text": "  MALIK, リルソフ, Swettyは今年出てもいいはずだけどね。まあ枠あるから。どうやって決めてるんだろう",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690988,
      "updated": 1774691139
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7a37a0000000000f85dd1",
      "text": "  大阪もあるしね、多分",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774691194,
      "updated": 1774691200
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c4e700000000007d2120",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/9594be61a3e20fbaa535e458a9f7549a][https://gyazo.com/8b0c215910c0af74c341252c7865b0c7][https://gyazo.com/db345479d80817646e118eae6f94e8e2]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774699751,
      "updated": 1774699821
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c52f00000000007d2126",
      "text": "  イーッヒッヒッヒッヒ🙌",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774699824,
      "updated": 1774699980
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c5dd00000000007d212b",
      "text": "  汚いサムネで申し訳ない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774699998,
      "updated": 1774700005
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c60f00000000007d212c",
      "text": "  画像蓋しとくか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700048,
      "updated": 1774700054
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ceb50000000000840544",
      "text": "  あ！かわい！[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1774702261,
      "updated": 1774702266
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7db0f0000000000837bc8",
      "text": "  それはもう[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774705423,
      "updated": 1774705923
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7eb420000000000f37fa7",
      "text": "  こういうものがあるのか[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1774709570,
      "updated": 1774709574
    },
    {
      "id": "69c837870000000000b3aa40",
      "text": "  おされ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1774729096,
      "updated": 1774729097
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c6db00000000007d2132",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/b6e77ec29d1c252edbe2235aadb8012a]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700252,
      "updated": 1774700254
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c6dd00000000007d2133",
      "text": "\t\tイマイロおでんつくっててすごい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700254,
      "updated": 1774700310
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c6e500000000007d2134",
      "text": "\t\t今日移転記念日で朝までやるぞとか書いてあるけどワンチャンいくか否か",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774700262,
      "updated": 1774700300
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c4dc00000000007d211f",
      "text": " 　ほたるいかのビリヤニ食べたい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774699741,
      "updated": 1774700410
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7dae70000000000837bc6",
      "text": " カニエのアルバム聴かないと",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774705384,
      "updated": 1774705393
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7daf00000000000837bc7",
      "text": " ツイッターにカニエのことYeって言ってる人急増しているように見えるがどうなのか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774705393,
      "updated": 1774705417
    },
    {
      "id": "69c79fc40000000000f85db6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774690245,
      "updated": 1774690544
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6acf0000000000084e55a",
      "text": "[2026-03-28]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774628080,
      "updated": 1774628083
    },
